comments.text: Over 50. 12 runs. Bowler: Megan Schutt. New Zealand Women: 9-236(rr 4.72)

Megan Schutt to Hayley Jensen. Yorker, Slog, False Shot to deep square leg for 1 run. Australia win a close one. New Zealand looked like they were cruising towards the target with Satterthwaite and Perkins at the crease before a game changing spell from Jess Jonassen, where she took 4 wickets, saw the White Ferns lose 47-5 to finish 6 runs short of their target.
